room_title: Escape room "The Cedar Lodge" by Mastermind Room Escape Challenge in Cedar City
room_address: 5 North Main Street, Suite 305 Cedar City, UT 84720
room_description: Participants enter The Cedar Lodge to check into a room for some fun and exciting times at a relaxing ski lodge when suddenly all avenues of escape are blocked! Was it an avalanche? Paranormal forces? A mentally unbalanced employee? The only way to know for sure is to work together through the ciphers, puzzles, codes and mazes to escape the room to freedom!
